        <b>2. Downloading the Virtual Machine (optional)</b>
        </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
        <td width="50%">
        <p>
        If your instructor specifies to use or you would like to take advantage of the RevEngE reverse engineering virtual machine, click on the "Tools" button under the "For Students" heading in the menu bar.  Follow the instructions on that page to install the virtual machine.  Note that running virtual machines is not possible on some hardware, such as Raspberry PIs. 
